{"tid":222476,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【又破紀錄】嘉湖山莊車位首破百萬 創屋苑新高","createTime":"2017-04-29T14:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T14:55:00.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b271d7a84985224577b0cf4c1eb4f6072ab0d1e0","tid":222476,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:23:26.000Z","msg":"天水圍嘉湖山莊樂湖居一個單號車位，剛以100萬元連租約成交，創屋苑單一車位新高價，兼首破百萬，比舊紀錄再貴5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產黃懷恩表示，該車位為樂湖居B1層單號車位，剛以100萬元成交，創屋苑單一車位歷史新高。據了解，買家為投資者，是基於車位連一份下年10月到期，月租達3,200元的租約而高價出手，比市值租金2,600元高逾兩成，購入車位後，可享3.8厘租金回報。<br />\n<br />\n原業主2014年以63萬元入市，賬面獲利37萬元，3年升值59%。嘉湖山莊目前約有60個車位放盤，入場費92萬元。嘉湖山莊對上一個高價車位，為翠湖居車位，2月以95萬元成交。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4C3D1d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4C3D1d0.jpg&h=e1d66658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56631508&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56631508%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170429&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kylKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=b1447c5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56631508%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170429&h=f6fc7be2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56631508&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170429</a>"},{"pid":"ae5ba80b6dc08f8b6290ef66b8d67f3efe456f6f","tid":222476,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:24:51.000Z","msg":"車位專家食屎啦"},{"pid":"c04bb6db7d8577e1b4b7e97267c77d3d370fe175","tid":222476,"uid":16085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:29:51.000Z","msg":"有咩產品高return得過車位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff05952e85a94c6c3cf4de26ed